WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:09.099 --> 00:00:16.099
Girl:

00:00:20.300 --> 00:00:25.160
When I was little grandpa used to have only
one foot and wouldn't go to the beach with me.

00:00:25.160 --> 00:00:30.989
Now he has two feet again and we can go
to the beach every summer.

00:00:30.989 --> 00:00:35.980
Grandpa still can't play soccer very well but I'm teaching him. You'll see.

00:00:35.980 --> 00:00:38.699
Grandpa:

00:00:38.699 --> 00:00:43.649
My granddaughter can be quite challenging.

00:00:43.649 --> 00:00:49.600
Without the limitation we can have a lot more fun together.

00:00:49.600 --> 00:00:56.600
Grandpa: My silicone foot is so easy to take care of.

00:01:10.500 --> 00:01:17.500
... and I can wear sandals again.

00:01:19.570 --> 00:01:26.570
... but the best thing is walking long distances

00:01:31.890 --> 00:01:37.219
is no longer a problem for me.

00:01:43.500 --> 00:01:50.500
Girl: I like grandpa's new foot.

00:01:53.979 --> 00:02:00.320
... and I like the new foot even better when

00:02:00.320 --> 00:02:02.769
I put some of mom's nail polish on it.

